 10. Important Notes

1. The self-hosted runner must have Docker installed and running.
2. The runner user must have permission to run Docker commands.
3. The GitOps token must have write access to the manifest repository.
4. The Trivy scan is configured for reporting only and will not fail the pipeline.
5. The runner labels in GitHub must match the labels used in the workflow.
6. Do not hardcode tokens in the workflow file. Always use GitHub Secrets.

