 11. Basic Troubleshooting Commands

 Check Runner Service

bash
systemctl list-units "actions.runner.*"


bash
sudo ./svc.sh status


 Check Docker

bash
docker ps
docker images


 Check Runner User Docker Permission

bash
sudo -u githubrunner docker ps


If the above command fails, add the runner user to the Docker group:

bash
sudo usermod -aG docker githubrunner


Then restart the runner service:

bash
sudo ./svc.sh stop
sudo ./svc.sh start


