 12. Final Outcome

After this implementation, the GitHub Actions pipeline will automatically build, scan, push, and update the Kubernetes manifest repository whenever changes are pushed to the application repository. This enables a GitOps-based CI/CD workflow where the latest image tag is automatically updated in the manifest repository for deployment.
